{"tid":1698773,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jennie 帶起了單眼皮鳳眼趨勢，登上醫生公開的整容範本排行榜","createTime":"2019-11-07T17:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T13:02:16.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e782c0b32ee389ccea004183c496cf2f3a8c5862","tid":1698773,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/popbee.com/image/2019/11/jj-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fpopbee.com%2Fimage%2F2019%2F11%2Fjj-1.jpg&h=c955dedf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對整容科技、風氣都相當發達的韓國來說，相關話題早已經是稀鬆平常的事情，亦是時常被搬上節目內容討論的主題，好比上回在綜藝節目《Video Star》便請來了各科醫生分享，身為整型外科代表的金鍾民醫師也順道公開了最常被「指名」的整容範本，除了像是宋慧喬、金泰熙、申敏兒等眾所皆知的女演員之外，還有三位女歌星的長相在近期也非常受歡迎，因此列出了 Top 3 排行榜，一起來看看吧！"},{"pid":"893d85d629252802442935c44d81570ea3bbe779","tid":1698773,"uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com/vp/3c5199a14d4d2fcc1b1a116a42b7570c/5E5AEE06/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/73420477_737074446767357_7883164617443166479_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F3c5199a14d4d2fcc1b1a116a42b7570c%2F5E5AEE06%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2Fs1080x1080%2F73420477_737074446767357_7883164617443166479_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D1&h=8b6405ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人氣超高的 Jennie 無疑帶起了一股「丹鳳眼」的流行，相對於一般標準的美人來說，像這樣更具個性、辨識度的長相，是現在許多女生所追求的方向，似乎也打破了過往一定要整成雙眼皮的唯一選擇。"},{"pid":"a47884e581c3c4f6f31de767eb12840e92a988dc","tid":1698773,"uid":44730,"like":29,"dislike":5,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:28:40.000Z","msg":"No. 2 潤娥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com/vp/c255ecf234dde18886289652d7085695/5E50E110/t51.2885-15/e35/70291235_2383191465343320_6441476606359970142_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2Fc255ecf234dde18886289652d7085695%2F5E50E110%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F70291235_2383191465343320_6441476606359970142_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D100&h=b5aa8510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生比喻登上第二名的潤娥就是「典型美人臉」的代表，包括了渾圓的大眼睛、堅挺的鼻子、鵝蛋的臉型都是許多客人指定的範本。"},{"pid":"a18d59562eea2834b2a13a0ae88743e0c11e93a0","tid":1698773,"uid":44730,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"No. 1 Irene<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com/vp/9c9bddb4d1d426bc05bf689a58621977/5E5B0524/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/72853486_976064302737566_3031102836053723908_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F9c9bddb4d1d426bc05bf689a58621977%2F5E5B0524%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2Fs1080x1080%2F72853486_976064302737566_3031102836053723908_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D1&h=3080bb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一名則是女團 Red Velvet 成員 Irene，醫生以「終極目標」來形容，便可以知道 Irene 的面貌在近期有多受韓國女生歡迎，原因是 Irene 的五官輪廓鮮明，不但亮眼更讓人過目難忘。"},{"pid":"7f08d9609ad8b2c57606e95447d552905c6b146a","tid":1698773,"uid":143093,"like":77,"dislike":7,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"俾咁多整Jennie咁嘅樣咁能戇居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3987dc148ae3950ae20ca7a34b2bebd16413c688","tid":1698773,"uid":52073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7f08d9609ad8b2c57606e95447d552905c6b146a","tid":1698773,"uid":143093,"like":77,"dislike":7,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"俾咁多整Jennie咁嘅樣咁能戇居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T17:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\